# API GOVERNANCE — tRPC

## Procedure Template
Every tRPC procedure MUST include:
1. Auth check (publicProcedure vs protectedProcedure vs federationAdminProcedure vs adminProcedure)
2. Input validation with Zod
3. Error handling (try/catch, TRPCError)
4. Consistent response shape

## Procedure Types
- publicProcedure — no auth
- protectedProcedure — any authenticated user
- federationAdminProcedure — federation_admin + input.federationId matches ctx.user.federationId
- adminProcedure — admin role only

## CRUD Coverage
For every resource: list, getById (or getBySlug), create, update, delete
- List: pagination, filtering
- Create/Update: federation scope for federation_admin

## External API Patterns
- Timeout on all fetch calls
- Retry for transient failures
- Verify webhook signatures (WhatsApp, Stripe)
